Your body…it might look and feel different from before. Or hey, it also might not! Sometimes I love mine and sometimes I hate it. Either way, remember it’s been through something absolutely freaking MAJOR. So maybe we can, at the very least, appreciate it more than we talk shit about it ❤️🙏🏼

All mom bods are good mom bods!😘🥰

Tried some relaxed fit jeans and the super popular faux leather pants! What do you think? Keep or return?

The Good: I got the right size! They fit just fine and as a skinny jean girl, I’m actually not mad at the relaxed fit!

The Not So Good: the waist isn’t as high rise and as snatched on me as I would prefer.  Feels like I’m going to have to take them on a test run before I can truly decide!

These are all in size 37W Long (= size 24) from Abercrombie. I’ve linked these in my LTK shop, link in my bio 💜 Follow my shop @theericalauren on the @shop.LTK app to shop this post and get exclusive upcoming app-only sales!!

Really trying to catch up on posting more work from this year 📸☺️😩 Had a legitimately fun day shooting with @fashionbrandcompany shot by @imcarolinaaa  Check them out by the way - super unique pieces up to and beyond 3X. 

And yes, that last dress does have 8 sleeves 😅🙀

Yeahhh I bought a lottt of stuff to try-on! 😆😫📦🛍️ Starting with activewear from Abercrombie - what do you think?? I really hope they will start carrying way more in XXXL+ site-wide, as I had to get all of these in XXL. But honestly, I’m pretty happy with the fit. 

Today (12/12) is the last day you can get 25% off at A&F by shopping with the @shop.ltk app! Link in my bio to my LTK page with all of the pieces from this haul linked for you ✨ #ltkxaf

Be seen. Take up space. Don’t be afraid to look silly. Live your life. You’re just as worthy as those you aspire to be as bold as. ❤️ 

I’ve held back my whole life, even now. Then sometimes I catch a moment of myself letting go and I see something I’m not used to seeing…me not caring how my body looks, not adjusting my clothes, not staying reserved hoping not to be called out or upon…. Let’s have more of those moments 🫶🏼
